<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d1817 0%, #5c1a1a 100%);
            border: 2px solid #d4af37;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #fff8dc;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #d4af37;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .message {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 3px solid #d4af37;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4af37, #b8941f);
            color: #2d1817 !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255, 248, 220, 0.7);
        }
        .expires {
            background: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .alt-link {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: rgba(255, 248, 220, 0.8);
        }
        .alt-link a {
            color: #d4af37;
            word-break: break-all;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ú® Mokhuba Club ‚ú®</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hola{% if invitee_name %} {{ invitee_name }}{% endif %},
            </div>

            <p>
                Has sido invitado{% if sender_name %} por <strong>{{ sender_name }}</strong>{% endif %} 
                a unirte a <strong>Mokhuba Club</strong>, un exclusivo espacio de membres√≠as premium.
            </p>

            {% if message %}
            <div class="message">
                {{ message }}
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{ acceptUrl }}" class="button" style="color: #2d1817 !important;">üëâ Completar mi Registro</a>
            </div>

            <div class="alt-link">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: rgba(255, 248, 220, 0.9);">
                    Si el bot√≥n no funciona, haz clic en este enlace:
                </p>
                <a href="{{ acceptUrl }}" style="color: #d4af37; word-break: break-all;">{{ acceptUrl }}</a>
            </div>

            <div class="expires">
                ‚è∞ Esta invitaci√≥n expira el: <strong>{{ expires_at|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</strong>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 248, 220, 0.8);">
                Si tienes alguna pregunta o problema para registrarte, 
                no dudes en contactarnos.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© {{ 'now'|date('Y') }} Mokhuba Club. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px;">
                Si no solicitaste esta invitaci√≥n, puedes ignorar este correo.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
